Package: spatialphy
Title: Spatial Phylogenetic Analyses in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew", "Kling", , "mkling@uvm.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9073-4240"))
Description: This package can be used to compute a variety of spatial phylogenetic metrics, using data on a phylogenetic tree and the geographic distributions of the terminal taxa. Functionality includes diversity metrics, turnover and biotic regionalization analyses, and spatial conservation prioritization.
